  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-6 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors are addressed: 11 factors are fully assessed with achieved levels meeting or exceeding required levels, and 2 factors are marked not-applicable with thorough rationale explaining why they fall outside the scope of this V&V 40 assessment. Decision: Accepted.",
